page.title: 20DOMESDAY SURVEY THANKS
page.content: {DOMESDAY SURVEY THANKS Domesday Survey Members of the public who were approached to help have been usually enthusiastic.It is felt that this page should be dedicated to thanking all who contributed.Editors Anne Vines and Patricia Duke-Cox Dot Batty P.17 Derek Marshall P.7,8 Hilda Curtis P.3 Roger Papworth P.4 Iris Daubney P.2 Dolly Patchett P.14 Patricia Duke-Cox P.1,16,19 James Inglis P.5 Bill Skelton P6,13,19 Rene Ismanycka P.15 David Tonge P11,12 Mary Jackson P9,10 Ann Vines P.18 Photographs were taken and developed by Terry Vines. Data Input by teachers and pupils of St.Hugh's School, Woodhall Spa: D.Radford,S.Jenkins, A.Hill,P.Miller, P.Maplethorpe,L.Goudeau,W.Boocock.
